{"tid":1516892,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港online 新職業 - 導遊] 發夢都想全民勇武!","createTime":"2019-08-29T17:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T03:18:54.000Z","uid":163604,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa86d60fbbed0710b4c66b1ab0bb96c8a7bfef5","tid":1516892,"uid":163604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:19:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">導遊公海TG: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/HTRM7lSSeKAfTC8Fc53q0g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FHTRM7lSSeKAfTC8Fc53q0g&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=df4b0440\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/HTRM7lSSeKAfTC8Fc53q0g</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8U4nTJd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8U4nTJd.gif&h=0a295adf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n導遊可以現場去執仔女教育 <br />\n雙方亦可於公海問答 <br />\n想行前? 搵導遊啦!<br />\n<br />\n勇武已經捱左三個月 和理非唔係無用 但前線俾人拉太多 勇武急需新血<br />\n眼見中後排和理非齊裝 試下行前少少 成為新晉勇武 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNKS1tU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNKS1tU.jpg&h=bd986ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新職業！導遊！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n要求：<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> 1. 口才 （要清晰講到注意事項俾新晉勇武知）</span><br />\n <span style=\"color: orange;\">2. 有基本局勢認知  速龍近身經驗</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 3. 去過最少5區參戰前線</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"> 4. full gear outlook 或 隨意</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>***有 家庭顧慮 / 有傷在身 / 攰 既勇武優先擔當</ins><br />\n<br />\n工作<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"> 1. 指導blackbloc/ 其他裝備 (耳仔, 耳仔, 耳仔)<br />\n 2. 前線職業介紹<br />\n 3. 警察種類教學（起碼要分到圓盾 長盾 速龍）<br />\n 4. 經驗分享 解釋不同情況既危險性（等佢地有個畫面先，要描述）<br />\n 5.   實地體驗（建議頭一兩次係安全時上第一排行一陣就夠 學下唔好見到狗就走）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">二轉 - 前線組別一覽</span></strong></span></span></span><br />\n下文前線細分 等各位二轉可以搵返合適崗位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">救人組<br />\n工作： 前線發生速龍捉人時 馬上救人</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ebDc0QR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FebDc0QR.png&h=ae786d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">盾手組<br />\n工作：擋子彈保護手足</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">打交組 - 徵求大量人手, 邊個淆底邊個就係鬼, 用人數打嬴對家, 嬴一次咁多啊!</span><br />\n工作：近戰對打速龍防暴</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjiHJGx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjiHJGx.gif&h=f0dd1fdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fXJXxzW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfXJXxzW.gif&h=dc23001b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JODAje1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJODAje1.gif&h=88ea1575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">消防組<br />\n工作：第二排執龍蛋 </span><br />\n<strong><strong>消防post</strong></strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1512180/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1512180/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">磚頭組<br />\n工作：速龍衝前時用磚打擊</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">彈射弓手組<br />\n工作： 掩護前排 遠程物理攻擊</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">魔法師組<br />\n工作：造成魔法／心理傷害</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HvsdfUQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvsdfUQ.jpg&h=f326cbae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BeWmZeY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBeWmZeY.gif&h=ae6f3dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">哨組<br />\n工作：留意敵方動靜 確保逃生路線</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">旗手組<br />\n工作：以旗代口 發出訊息</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1512051/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1512051/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jMfjpuJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjMfjpuJ.png&h=0d5cc2d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">大聲公組<br />\n工作：傳遞哨組哨兵tg消息 確保人群之間有足夠距離 唔會阻礙逃生</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">物資組<br />\n工作：係後方確保物資充足 要同前排溝通所需物資</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">工程組<br />\n工作：你估下？hehe</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190825/_2019082515014045036.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190825%2F_2019082515014045036.jpg&h=7ea74b1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人話和理非拎哂啲裝 但勇武無介意過 等緊你地有一日會加入勇武！<br />\n再次呼籲和理非 如果已經齊裝 係時候嘗試勇武 你地有無限可能！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1J0a2By.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1J0a2By.png&h=3326624a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光</span><span style=\"color: green;\">復</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">香</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">港</span>！<span style=\"color: violet;\">時</span><span style=\"color: pink;\">代</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">革</span><span style=\"color: teal;\">命</span>！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">導遊公海TG: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/HTRM7lSSeKAfTC8Fc53q0g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FHTRM7lSSeKAfTC8Fc53q0g&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=df4b0440\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/HTRM7lSSeKAfTC8Fc53q0g</a></span>"},{"pid":"0844b3e42f0716c6eea3c3a785e26377c58c53b7","tid":1516892,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:20:05.000Z","msg":"有Tw